---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<div class="relative mt-32 mb-12 space-y-24 isolate">
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-cyan-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 dark:opacity-20 pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center px-4 relative">
        <div
            class="absolute -top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20"
        >
        </div>
        <h2
            class="relative text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8 tracking-tight"
        >
            Cómo Sincronizar y Arreglar <br class="hidden md:block" />
            <span
                class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 via-blue-500 to-indigo-600"
                >Subtítulos SRT Desfasados</span
            >
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-light max-w-3xl mx-auto"
        >
            Herramienta online gratuita para <strong>corregir el tiempo</strong> de tus archivos de subtítulos
            (.srt). Adelanta o retrasa los diálogos en segundos o milisegundos fácilmente. <strong
                class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-200"
                >Sin instalar programas</strong
            > y compatible con todos los reproductores.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h3
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-6 py-2 rounded-full bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800/50 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 font-bold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
            >
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 animate-pulse"></span>
                Diagnóstico del Problema
            </h3>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 dark:shadow-black/40 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-cyan-500/5 rounded-bl-full -mr-8 -mt-8 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150 duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-100 to-blue-50 dark:from-cyan-900/30 dark:to-blue-900/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-6 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:filmstrip" class="text-3xl" />
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
                    Caos de Framerates
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Cine (24fps) vs TV (25fps) vs NTSC (23.976fps). Una simple conversión errónea
                    hace que los subtítulos "patinen" y se alejen cada vez más del audio.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 dark:shadow-black/40 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-500/5 rounded-bl-full -mr-8 -mt-8 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150 duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-100 to-fuchsia-50 dark:from-purple-900/30 dark:to-fuchsia-900/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 mb-6 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:content-cut" class="text-3xl" />
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
                    Director's Cut
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Versiones extendidas con escenas extra. Si tus subtítulos son para la versión de
                    cine, el desfase no será constante: saltará bruscamente en bloques.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl shadow-slate-200/50 dark:shadow-black/40 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-emerald-500/5 rounded-bl-full -mr-8 -mt-8 transition-transform group-hover:scale-150 duration-700"
                >
                </div>

                <div
                    class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-100 to-teal-50 dark:from-emerald-900/30 dark:to-teal-900/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 mb-6 group-hover:rotate-6 transition-transform"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:timer-off-outline" class="text-3xl" />
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
                    Intros Fantasma
                </h4>
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Logos de productoras o explicaciones previas que duran diferente. Generan un <strong
                        >desfase estático</strong
                    > perfecto para corregir con esta herramienta.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-12 text-center">
            Protocolo de Ajuste
        </h3>

        <div
            class="relative space-y-8 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:left-8 md:before:left-1/2 before:-ml-px before:h-full before:w-0.5 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:from-transparent before:via-cyan-200 before:dark:via-cyan-900 before:to-transparent"
        >
            <div class="relative flex items-center md:justify-between group">
                <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                        Identifica el 'Anchor'
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2">
                        Busca una frase corta y sonora, como un portazo o un grito, fácil de
                        localizar en audio.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -ml-3 md:-ml-4 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-slate-900 shadow-lg z-10"
                >
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:w-5/12 pl-4 md:pl-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm md:shadow-none md:bg-transparent md:border-0"
                >
                    <div class="md:hidden mb-2">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                            Identifica el 'Anchor'
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <span
                        class="text-sm font-mono text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/20 px-2 py-1 rounded"
                        >Ej: "¡Cuidado!"</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-center md:justify-between md:flex-row-reverse group">
                <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12 text-left pl-8">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                        Calcula el Delta
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2">
                        Resta el tiempo de audio menos el tiempo del subtítulo. Esa diferencia es tu <strong
                            >offset</strong
                        >.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -ml-3 md:-ml-4 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-500 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-slate-900 shadow-lg z-10"
                >
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:w-5/12 pr-4 md:pr-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm md:shadow-none md:bg-transparent md:border-0 text-left md:text-right"
                >
                    <div class="md:hidden mb-2">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                            Calcula el Delta
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                        Audio: 00:10 | Subtítulo: 00:12
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white">
                        Diferencia: 2 seg
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative flex items-center md:justify-between group">
                <div class="hidden md:block w-5/12 text-right pr-8">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                        Aplica la Corrección
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2">
                        Introduce el valor en la herramienta. Positivo para retrasar, negativo para
                        adelantar.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 -ml-3 md:-ml-4 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 md:w-8 md:h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 ring-4 ring-white dark:ring-slate-900 shadow-lg z-10"
                >
                    <Icon name="mdi:check" class="text-white text-xs" />
                </div>
                <div
                    class="ml-20 md:ml-0 md:w-5/12 pl-4 md:pl-8 py-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800 shadow-sm md:shadow-none md:bg-transparent md:border-0"
                >
                    <div class="md:hidden mb-2">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                            Aplica la Corrección
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-2">
                        <span
                            class="px-2 py-1 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 text-red-700 dark:text-red-300 rounded text-xs font-bold"
                            >- Adelantar</span
                        >
                        <span
                            class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 rounded text-xs font-bold"
                            >+ Retrasar</span
                        >
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-20">
        <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-white dark:from-slate-900/50 dark:to-slate-900 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/50 shadow-xl"
        >
            <h3
                class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-2"
            >
                <Icon name="mdi:lightbulb-on-outline" class="text-yellow-500" />
                Preguntas Frecuentes
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <details class="group marker:content-['']">
                    <summary
                        class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:text-cyan-600 dark:hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors font-medium"
                    >
                        ¿Qué es el "Drift" progresivo?
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:chevron-down"
                            class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400"
                        />
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    >
                        Ocurre cuando el desajuste aumenta con el tiempo. Comienza bien, pero a la
                        hora de película tienes 5 segundos de retraso. Esto requiere conversión de
                        framerate, no solo desplazamiento.
                    </p>
                </details>

                <div class="h-px bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800"></div>

                <details class="group marker:content-['']">
                    <summary
                        class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 hover:text-cyan-600 dark:hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors font-medium"
                    >
                        ¿Mis archivos están seguros?
                        <Icon
                            name="mdi:chevron-down"
                            class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-slate-400"
                        />
                    </summary>
                    <p
                        class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-4 border-l-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    >
                        Sí. Toda la magia ocurre en tu navegador usando JavaScript. El archivo nunca
                        sale de tu ordenador. Privacidad absoluta garantizada.
                    </p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
